{"tid":1828524,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張建宗稱十項民生措施料下年中落實","createTime":"2020-01-18T02:42:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T05:18:28.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c28f8c7aca46f3a318d80df5ac6183b05106c015","tid":1828524,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T02:42:08.000Z","msg":"政務司司長張建宗出席電台節目表示，早前政府公佈十項民生措施是結構性改革，並非小修小補，顯示政府銳意處理深層次矛盾。十項民生措施估計在<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2021年中</span></strong>落實。對於有關措施，能否在財委會獲通過，張建宗說，對此有信心，相信惠及民生的措施可以通過。他說議員在立法會拉布是政治現實一部分，希望市民諒解。<br />\n<br />\n另外，他表示政府不怕被指「今天的我打倒昨天的我」，今次盤點多年勞工福利問題，想「實事做好，好事做實」。擴大2元乘車優惠受惠人數，涉及額外17億開支，他指此措施無分階級，中產也能受惠。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503479-20200118.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503479-20200118.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKAsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=0b292b3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503479-20200118.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=79af0a2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503479-20200118.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"3abe5e3daab786015e517ad1e126af4a57da3966","tid":1828524,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T02:42:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5352ab18418dff8bac4b1cf49967d6f2b98d913","tid":1828524,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T02:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmo